examples.en: The cliff was shrouded in mist.
The work is shrouded in secrecy.
Joseph was shrouded under a dark blanket.
Their work is shrouded in secrecy.
The incident has always been shrouded in mystery.
examples.ru: Это происшествие всегда было окутано тайной.

examples.en: A shroud of silence surrounded the general's death.
examples.ru: Смерть генерала была окружена завесой молчания.

examples.en: The mountains were shrouded in fog.
The fog rolled in, and a grey shroud covered the city.
examples.ru: Туман сгустился, и город накрыла серая пелена.
